{
  "stem": "8842.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'm driving myself crazy many times to remember that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--it was near--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, which was a very famous resort.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that was a little bit further, closer to the city in the woods.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was just a camp, just a plain simple camp for children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had an outstanding time there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it was-- everybody was just going crazy there and enjoying their own things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was singing a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were playing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we made shows.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we made all kind of-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] everything that belonged in the music world.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one night, just while we were sleeping, we heard terrible bombing and, and explosions.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And disastrous fright fell in all of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we woke up from all this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And our teachers, rather-- what do they call them?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- whoever took care of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--counselors--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--told us to get fast-- we should get dressed fast and leave everything behind.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we have to evacuate the place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Something is happening in Kovno, which we are not too far-- we were not too far away from there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Actually, what was happening is the Germans bombed the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] where the airplanes are standing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm going to have a problem remembering words now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The airport.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they bombed the whole airport.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was not too far where we were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we heard it very strongly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was the day that opened-- that opened-- that was June-- July the 22nd, 1941.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is when actually the Germans started to get-- go closer to Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1939, our parents started to tell us that something is happening terribly in-- between the Germans and the Russians.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
